thread.title_full: Merchant One reviewed by Bo Prock

author: Bo Prock
title: Bo Prock
text: Morning Star was a fabulous representation of your company. I will admit I am still a little irritated about the 24.50 charge that I have been getting every month and not sure that I was informed previously as to what it was for but she helped me to make sure that it will not happen again so I am in a good mood for a Monday. Thanks again.
